                    "target": "所有简单武器"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick can take the Help action as a bonus action.",
                    "target": "随从可以将协助动作作为奖励动作来执行。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "On its turn in combat, the sidekick can take the Dash, Disengage, or Hide action as a bonus action.",
                    "target": "在战斗中自己的回合，随从可以将疾走、脱离或躲藏动作作为奖励动作来执行。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Choose two of the sidekick's skill proficiencies. The sidekick's proficiency bonus is doubled for any ability check it makes that uses any of the chosen proficiencies.",
                    "target": "选择随从的两项技能熟练项。随从在进行使用所选熟练项的任何属性检定时，其熟练加值翻倍。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick increases one ability score of your choice by 2, or the sidekick increases two ability scores of your choice by 1. The sidekick can't increase an ability score above 20 using this feature.",
                    "target": "随从将你选择的一项属性值提高2，或将你选择的两项属性值各提高1。随从不能通过此特性将属性值提高到20以上。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick can take the Help action as a bonus action. When using this feature to aid an ally in attacking a creature, that target can be up to 30 feet away from the sidekick, and the sidekick can deal an extra 2d6 damage to it the next time the sidekick hits it with an attack roll before the end of the current turn. The extra damage is the same type of damage dealt by the attack.",
                    "target": "随从可以将协助动作作为奖励动作来执行。使用此特性协助盟友攻击一名生物时，该目标最多可离随从30英尺，并且在当前回合结束前，随从下一次以攻击掷骰命中该目标时可对其造成额外2d6伤害。额外伤害的类型与该次攻击造成的伤害类型相同。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "When the sidekick is subjected to an effect that allows it to make a Dexterity saving throw to take only half damage, it instead takes no damage if it succeeds on the saving throw, and only half damage if it failed. The sidekick doesn't benefit from this feature while incapacitated.",
                    "target": "当随从受到允许进行敏捷豁免以仅承受一半伤害的效果时，若豁免成功则不受伤害，若豁免失败则仅承受一半伤害。随从在失能时无法从此特性中受益。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "When the sidekick takes the Help action, the creature who receives the help also gains a 1d6 bonus to the d20 roll. If that roll is an attack roll, the creature can forgo adding the bonus to it, and then if the attack hits, the creature can add the bonus to the attack's damage roll against one target.",
                    "target": "当随从执行协助动作时，接受协助的生物的d20掷骰也获得1d6加值。若该次掷骰为攻击掷骰，该生物可以放弃将该加值加在攻击掷骰上，若攻击命中，则该生物可将该加值加到针对一个目标的攻击伤害掷骰上。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Whenever the sidekick makes an ability check that includes its whole proficiency bonus, it can treat a d20 roll of 9 or lower as a 10.",
                    "target": "每当随从进行包含其完整熟练加值的属性检定时，它可以将d20掷骰结果为9或更低视为10。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Sharp Mind: The sidekick gains proficiency in one saving throw of your choice.",
                    "target": "敏锐心智：随从获得你选择的一项豁免检定的熟练项。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "When the sidekick takes the Help action, the creature who receives the help also gains a 2d6 bonus to the d20 roll. If that roll is an attack roll, the creature can forgo adding the bonus to it, and then if the attack hits, the creature can add the bonus to the attack's damage roll against one target.",
                    "target": "当随从采取帮助动作时，受到帮助的生物还会在d20检定上获得2d6加值。如果该检定是攻击检定，生物可以放弃将该加值加到检定上，然后若攻击命中，生物可以将该加值加到该次攻击对一个目标的伤害掷骰上。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick gains gain proficiency in one saving throw of your choice",
                    "target": "随从获得你选择的一项豁免检定的熟练项。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick gains the ability to cast spells. Choose the Spellcaster's role: Mage, Healer, or Prodigy. This choice determines the spell list and spellcasting ability used by the sidekick.",
                    "target": "随从获得施法能力。选择施法者的角色：法师、治疗者或神童。该选择决定随从使用的法术列表和施法属性。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Spell List: Wizard - Spellcasting Ability: Intelligence",
                    "target": "法术列表：法师 - 施法属性：智力"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Spell Lists: Cleric and Druid - Spellcasting Ability: Wisdom",
                    "target": "法术列表：牧师与德鲁伊 - 施法属性：感知"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Spell Lists: Bard and Warlock - Spellcasting Ability: Charisma",
                    "target": "法术列表：吟游诗人与邪术师 - 施法属性：魅力"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick can add its spellcasting ability modifier to the damage it deals with any cantrip.",
                    "target": "随从可以将其施法属性调整值加到其任意戏法造成的伤害上。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Choose one school of magic. Whenever the sidekick casts a spell of that school by expending a spell slot, the sidekick can add its spellcasting ability modifier to the spell's damage roll or healing roll, if any.",
                    "target": "选择一个魔法学派。每当随从通过消耗法术位施放该学派的法术时，若有，则随从可以将其施法属性调整值加到该法术的伤害掷骰或治疗掷骰上。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Taking damage can't break the sidekick's concentration on a spell.",
                    "target": "受到伤害不会打断随从对法术的专注。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick gains proficiency in two skills of your choice",
                    "target": "随从获得你选择的两项技能的熟练项。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "all armor",
                    "target": "所有护甲"
