                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Each warrior focuses on offense or defense in their training. Choose one of the following options:",
                    "target": "每位战士在训练中专注于进攻或防御。选择以下选项之一："
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick gains a + 2 bonus to all attack rolls (already included).",
                    "target": "随从的所有攻击检定获得 +2 加值（已包含）。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick can use its reaction to impose disadvantage on the attack roll of a creature within 5 feet of it whose target isn't the sidekick, provided the sidekick can see the attacker.",
                    "target": "如果随从能看见攻击者，它可以用其反应使 5 英尺内目标不是随从的生物的攻击检定具有劣势。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "Once per short or long rest, the sidekick can use a bonus action on its turn to regain hit points equal to 1d10 + its level in this class.",
                    "target": "每次短休或长休后一次，随从可以在其回合用一个附赠动作恢复等于 1d10 + 它在该职业等级的生命值。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick's attack rolls score a critical hit on a roll of 19 or 20 on the d20.",
                    "target": "随从的攻击检定在 d20 掷出 19 或 20 时造成重击。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick can attack twice, instead of once, whenever it takes the Attack action on its turn. If the sidekick has the Multiattack action, it can use Extra Attack or Multiattack on a turn, not both.",
                    "target": "随从在其回合进行攻击动作时可攻击两次，而非一次。如果随从拥有多重攻击动作，则其在一个回合中可使用额外攻击或多重攻击，不能同时使用。"
                },
                {
                    "type": "ObjectProperty",
                    "name": "desc",
                    "source": "The sidekick has advantage on initiative rolls.",
